This directory contains the following examples of pointers

File      Demonstrates
--------  -------------------------------------------------------
ex1.cpp   simple pointer usage showing basic syntax
ex2.cpp   pointer to an array of int, consider an array a const pointer
ex3.cpp   pointer to an array of char (CString)
ex4.cpp   dynamic allocation of memory, dangling pointer
ex5.cpp   dynamic allocation of an array
ex6.cpp   pointer to a struct and -> operator
ex7.cpp   dynamic allocation of a struct
ex8.cpp   pointer to a class object and dynamic allocation of an object
ex9.cpp   pointer to a dynamically allocated  array of class objects
ex10.cpp  passing a pointer as an argument to a function
ex11.cpp  pointer as pass by reference and function returning a pointer
